high_descs: Turn and walk past the coffee table, hanging a right once you pass it, and walk up to the white stand that is to the left of the television.
Pick up the figurine that is on the left side of the white stand.
Turn to your right and walk, hang a right just before you reach the dining table, then walk up to the floor lamp.
Turn on the lamp
anns.task_desc: Inspect a figurine using the light of a lamp.

high_descs: Go across room to stand in front of white table.
Pick up statue from the left side of the white table.
Turn around, go across room to the lamp.
Turn on the lamp while holding the statue.
anns.task_desc: Carry a statue across room and turn on lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the table to the left of the TV.
Pick up the statue from the table.
Turn around and go to the lamp by the door.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine the statue by the lamp.

high_descs: Move to the end table to the left of the TV.
Pick up the statue from the table.
Move to the lamp on the left of the couch.
Turn on the lamp in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Inspect the statue on the end table next to the TV with a lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and go to stand in front of the white table with the statue on it.
Pick the statue up from the table.
Turn around and go to the lamp to the left of the couch.
Turn the lamp on.
anns.task_desc: Turn a lamp on with a statue in hand.

high_descs: Turn around and walk past the coffee table to the small white table by the TV stand
Pick up the statue from the white table
Turn and walk around the coffee table to the floor lamp by the sofa
Turn on the floor lamp
anns.task_desc: Examine the statue under the light of the floor lamp
